Class AbstractFormatHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.ldap.AbstractFormatHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FormatHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DSMLFormatHandler, LDIFFormatHandler

    public abstract class AbstractFormatHandler
extends Object
implements FormatHandler
    Abstract base class for FormatHandler objects that import/export directory entries to/from LDAP directory servers in LDIF and DSML format.
    Since:
    1.2.0
